Suggested usage:

Install followings packages
      pyflakes
      python-mode
      python-ropemacs

Create a new folder in your home directory
      $ mkdir ~/emacs.rc

Clone git repository into this directory
      $ cd ~/emacs.rc
      $ git clone git://github.com/dirtybit/Emacs-Conf.git

Copy pycomplete.py into PYTHONPATH
      $ cp ~/emacs.rc/Emacs-Conf/emacs.d/pycomplete.py $PYTHONPATH/

Link necessary files
      $ cd
      $ ln -s ~/emacs.rc/Emacs-Conf/emacs.d .emacs.d
      $ ln -s ~/emacs.rc/Emacs-Conf/dot-emacs .emacs